{"id":4014,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/4014","type":2,"name":"ストレンヂア 無皇刃譚","name_cn":"异邦人 无皇刃谭","summary":"　　在天下失序、列强割据的战乱时代，僧人祥庵将一名孤儿从中国带到了日本。孤儿名叫仔太郎，他背负着一个惊人的秘密。与祥庵失散后，孤苦无依的仔太郎带着爱犬飞丸前往赤池之国的万觉寺，在途中遇见了神秘剑士“无名”。仔太郎遭到追杀，危急时刻无名救了他一命。从此两人结伴同行。性格乖僻的浪人和紧闭心扉的少年虽然磕磕碰碰不断，但渐渐成了好朋友。\r\n　　白鸾率领的追杀组织还是抓住了仔太郎，他们开始着手筹备某种仪式。金发碧眼的剑士“罗狼”也是追杀组织中的一员，他虽然听命行事但并不真正在意组织的目的，对他来说，寻找可以与自己匹敌的对手才是生命的意义。罗狼与无名之间的生死对决拉开了帷幕……","eps":[{"id":155908,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/155908","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"ストレンヂア 無皇刃譚","name_cn":"异邦人 无皇刃谭","duration":"102m","airdate":"2007-09-29","comment":5,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2007-09-29","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":2944,"count":{"1":0,"2":4,"3":7,"4":5,"5":30,"6":140,"7":572,"8":1503,"9":535,"10":148},"score":7.9},"rank":255,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/1c/df/4014_e6u34.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1c/df/4014_e6u34.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1c/df/4014_e6u34.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/1c/df/4014_e6u34.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/1c/df/4014_e6u34.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":924,"collect":3888,"doing":50,"on_hold":73,"dropped":15},"crt":[{"id":26072,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/26072","name":"名無し","name_cn":"无名","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/9c/bd/26072_crt_00P2z.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/9c/bd/26072_crt_00P2z.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/9c/bd/26072_crt_00P2z.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9c/bd/26072_crt_00P2z.jpg"},"comment":2,"collects":18,"info":{"name_cn":"无名","alias":{"zh":"无名氏","kana":"ななし"},"gender":"男"},"actors":[{"id":15373,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/15373","name":"長瀬智也","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/99/de/15373_prsn_Gv4mX.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/99/de/15373_prsn_Gv4mX.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/99/de/15373_prsn_Gv4mX.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/99/de/15373_prsn_Gv4mX.jpg"}}]},{"id":7